1
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:07,500
♪That dangerous temptation♪

2
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,020
♪Like a whirlpool churning deep♪

3
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:12,900
♪Like a moth darts into the flame♪

4
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:14,340
♪Falling towards the light♪

5
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:17,420
♪Watch as everything drowns in shadows♪

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,340
♪Have no fear, do not retreat♪

7
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:23,220
♪See the blazing sparks ignite♪

8
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:27,060
♪Believe this all has cause and effect♪

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,460
♪No evil escapes untouched♪

10
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,820
♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

11
00:00:32,060 --> 00:00:34,850
♪The memories howl as they flash by♪

12
00:00:34,850 --> 00:00:37,820
[Miss Mystery]

13
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:39,320
[Lianhe Police Station]
Reporting for duty!

14
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:40,160
Come in.

15
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:49,800
Now that I've given you

16
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,760
the position of Chief Detective,

17
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:54,440
you must work diligently
and get things done for me.

18
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,280
Yes, Sir!

19
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:58,680
Receiving your trust
is my honor, Mr. Mayor!

20
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:01,360
I will spare no effort and remain loyal!

21
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:02,480
Alright.

22
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,920
Enough fancy words.

23
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:11,520
Remember,

24
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,880
and remember forever

25
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:18,480
who your owner is.

26
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,960
Since you chose to be a lackey,

27
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,760
act like one.

28
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:30,980
[Episode 12]

29
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,680
You're awake!

30
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,600
Yes.

31
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,560
How did I do yesterday?

32
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,000
Yesterday...

33
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,680
I fell asleep, so I don't remember.

34
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,480
It was fine.

35
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,400
That sounds right.

36
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,920
Give me a second.
The coffee is almost ready.

37
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:50,920
Bao'er,

38
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,400
for a long time,

39
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,320
I haven't been drinking coffee.

40
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,200
Why?

41
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:03,200
When I was little,

42
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,920
my mom used to like coffee,

43
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,840
just like this.

44
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,080
Watching her drinking coffee,

45
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,280
I wanted to taste it too.

46
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,880
My mom couldn't stop me,

47
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,800
so she added some sugar

48
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,000
to the coffee,

49
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,240
telling me

50
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,320
that coffee is sweet.

51
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,000
But after she passed away,

52
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,960
I realized...

53
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,240
Oh,

54
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,840
turns out coffee is bitter.

55
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,480
So,

56
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,720
I stopped drinking coffee
ever since then.

57
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,120
I'm sorry, Guanwen.

58
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:46,280
Then let's forget about coffee today.

59
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,080
It's fine.

60
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,160
Bao'er,

61
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:55,840
lately,

62
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,280
I'm especially grateful to fate,

63
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,400
because having you

64
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,880
has added some sweetness

65
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:04,800
to my bitter life.

66
00:04:05,140 --> 00:04:07,420
♪It seems to be changing♪

67
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:10,980
♪The familiar yet strange face♪

68
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:13,500
♪I want to get close♪

69
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:17,180
♪To those once bright eyes♪

70
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,960
Taste it.

71
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:23,100
♪Unable to touch♪

72
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:26,780
♪Between us♪

73
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,200
Sweet?

74
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,120
Tasty.

75
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:38,460
♪Looking away from you♪

76
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,640
Actually, I should thank you.

77
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,320
I originally thought
after my parents' death,

78
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,000
there would be no more joy

79
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,800
in my dreary life.

80
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:50,660
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

81
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:54,000
Little did I expect
God would give me a piece of candy,

82
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,560
which is you.

83
00:04:57,540 --> 00:05:00,100
♪Flitting images flashing♪

84
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:03,060
♪Eyes fall shut♪

85
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:06,540
♪Fingertips gently touched♪

86
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:09,860
♪Risking fate and danger venturing♪

87
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:11,820
♪Dancing on the tip of the knife♪

88
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:17,380
♪Put on a show wholeheartedly♪

89
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:22,100
♪In a moment♪

90
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:24,860
♪The memory in my mind♪

91
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,900
♪Surging at me♪

92
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:31,060
♪Beliefs hidden deep inside♪

93
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:34,340
♪In an abyss perhaps inescapable♪

94
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:37,820
♪Under a ray of light in the darkness♪

95
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:40,220
♪I may reopen my eyes♪

96
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:55,280
We don't know
what is up with Southeast Asia,

97
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,400
and they won't let us through this time.

98
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,200
But please rest assured.

99
00:05:58,320 --> 00:06:00,120
I can solve the problem these days.

100
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,640
Father,

101
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:03,840
Mr. Dou.

102
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,920
The shipment to Southeast Asia
has been cleared by customs.

103
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,080
Wha-

104
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,160
Really?

105
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,520
I've heard you talk about it.

106
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,640
Our goods in Southeast Asia
are always getting held up by customs.

107
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,040
It just so happens my father
has some connections in Southeast Asia,

108
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,480
so I made a call
and pulled some strings to help out.

109
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,200
Well,

110
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:26,720
in the future, we'll inevitably have
more dealings with Southeast Asia.

111
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,760
I think we should
hand the Southeast Asia route

112
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,600
over to Bao'er from now on.

113
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,880
I need to consider your decision.

114
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,640
After all,
Ms. Lin is new to the business.

115
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,040
She is bound to be inexperienced
in some areas of the work.

116
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:47,800
Also, Ms. Lin is not a local.

117
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,880
That is not accurate.

118
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:52,160
Since Bao'er took over
the shipping company,

119
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:56,080
the operations have been
much smoother than under Qian Tong.

120
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:57,760
Of course,

121
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:01,760
this is also thanks
to your wise judgment.

122
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,400
Thank you, Father.

123
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,440
Thank you, Mr. Dou.

124
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,720
I need to leave now.

125
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:07,800
Go.

126
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,360
Dou,

127
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:17,320
come here with Lili for a meal someday.

128
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,600
Let us old folks enjoy tea,

129
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:24,280
raise birds, and live in comfort.
Doesn't that sound nice?

130
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:25,640
But...

131
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:28,320
Look how carefree the bird lives!

132
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,160
Tweet, tweet!

133
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:38,200
[BABY RESTAURANT]

134
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,000
Baby.

135
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,200
Baby.

136
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:42,320
Bao'er,

137
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,520
don't you love this restaurant?

138
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,280
I bought this place for you as a gift.

139
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:50,320
From now on,
you can make me coffee every day.

140
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,520
What about the Blooming House?

141
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,000
Blooming House?

142
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,640
I'll get rid of it.

143
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:59,080
I will only do whatever you like.

144
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,680
Alright, just spit it.

145
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,640
What exactly do you want?

146
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:05,120
Nice, I can't hide anything from you.

147
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:06,600
Actually,

148
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,320
I'm worried about you.

149
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:11,240
My dad and Mr. Dou's business is shady.

150
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,600
I don't want you to be in danger.

151
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,600
You know

152
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,040
that I have no choice

153
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,760
but to get to this point.

154
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,040
Okay.

155
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,680
Since you insist on doing this,

156
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,280
I will do it with you.

157
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,440
If your next target is Mr. Dou,

158
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,400
I will help you.

159
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:37,880
Okay.

160
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,560
I promise you

161
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:40,840
to face them together.

162
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:51,700
[BABY RESTAURANT]

163
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,360
Father.

164
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,840
I knew
there was more to this Lin Bao'er.

165
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,000
How surprising!

166
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,000
It's too late to make any remarks now.

167
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,960
How much have we got on Lin Bao'er?

168
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,520
No need to rush.

169
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,480
Let's just sit back and enjoy the show.

170
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:39,860
♪The end has now been reached♪

171
00:09:40,140 --> 00:09:42,780
